title: N5 [RNA-Seq]
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was extracted using TRIZOL protocol (Life Technologies). Sequencing library was constructed using Illumina mRNA-Seq Sample Preparation protocol.
data_processing: paired-end/ single-end 36-base pair (bp) reads were filtered based on qseq score
data_processing.1: Reads were the subjected to Illumina RNA-seq pipeline (CASAVA 1.7) for RNA-seq analysis, aligned using Hg19 genome as reference, and all default parameters for alignment
data_processing.2: From the raw gene counts, normaliation for each gene was done to obtain the number of mapped bases per 1 million aligned bases
data_processing.4: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: Excel sheet, RNA expression level of selected genes.
contact_address: School of Laboratory Medicine and Life Sciences
